  "title": "Containerizing ETL Jobs Using FastAPI with Python 3.12+",
  "summary": "This guide demonstrates how to containerize ETL (Extract, Transform, Load) jobs using FastAPI, a modern, fast (high-performance), web framework for building APIs with Python 3.12+ and Starlette under the hood.",
  "key_points": [
    "FastAPI provides an intuitive, easy-to-use, and efficient way to build APIs",
    "Using containers allows for portable, scalable, and reproducible ETL job deployments",
